attributes.Long form description: The student disassembles a table. He first unscrews the top hex socket head from the four legs and disassembles the top table. Then he unscrews the bottom hex socket head from the first leg and disassembles it. After he unscrews the bottom hex socket head from the second leg and disassembles it, then unscrews the top hex socket head from the third leg and disassembles it, and finally, he unscrews the top hex socket head from the fourth leg and disassembles it.
